{"tid":731393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[刁大大]「潑墨女孩」下落不明　網友仿效行動 肇慶習近平宣傳畫像被塗泥漿","createTime":"2018-07-06T06:49:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T07:36:41.000Z","uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"64b21c5c626c40d7ad8ac0fb5f83b7c1cf1a3815","tid":731393,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T06:49:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%BD%91%E5%A2%A8%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9-%E4%B8%8B%E8%90%BD%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E-%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E4%BB%BF%E6%95%88%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95-%E8%82%87%E6%85%B6%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E7%95%AB%E5%83%8F%E8%A2%AB%E5%A1%97%E6%B3%A5%E6%BC%BF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25BD%2591%25E5%25A2%25A8%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%25A9-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%2590%25BD%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%258E-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%258F%258B%25E4%25BB%25BF%25E6%2595%2588%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595-%25E8%2582%2587%25E6%2585%25B6%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%2583%258F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25A1%2597%25E6%25B3%25A5%25E6%25BC%25BF%2F&d=GPWZBtuTsridr%2BxWHMGzFWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=8dbe9275\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25BD%2591%25E5%25A2%25A8%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%25A9-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%2590%25BD%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%258E-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%258F%258B%25E4%25BB%25BF%25E6%2595%2588%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595-%25E8%2582%2587%25E6%2585%25B6%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%2583%258F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25A1%2597%25E6%25B3%25A5%25E6%25BC%25BF%2F&h=3ba2648b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%BD%91%E5%A2%A8%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9-%E4%B8%8B%E8%90%BD%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E-%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E4%BB%BF%E6%95%88%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95-%E8%82%87%E6%85%B6%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E7%95%AB%E5%83%8F%E8%A2%AB%E5%A1%97%E6%B3%A5%E6%BC%BF/</a><br />\n<br />\n上海日前有年青女子向國家主席習近平肖像潑墨，高呼「反對獨裁暴政等口號」，更將影片上載至Twitter，其後被警察帶走，下落不明。其抗議行動引發網友仿效，廣東有人在習近平宣傳板上，塗上泥漿。<br />\n<br />\n《自由亞洲電台》報道，該名女子被網民封為「潑墨女孩」，事件發生後，「潑墨」立刻成為大陸網絡禁詞，其抗議行動持續在網絡上發酵，更引發網友仿效。有網友倡議模仿「潑墨女孩」塗抹習近平像，以行動對抗中共的「造神運動」，希望透過施壓促使「潑墨女孩」獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n有匿名網友昨日（5日）上傳一張照片，指相中是廣東肇慶一幅繪有習近平畫像的宣傳板，習的鼻子及嘴巴被塗上泥漿。有海外民運人士，計劃仿效「潑墨女孩」，到當地的中國使領館前，對習近平像以塗鴉進行抗議。《自由亞洲電台》報道，有維權律師將會為「潑墨女孩」提供法律援助。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/xi-08_gwPEv_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fxi-08_gwPEv_1200x0.png&h=e4ef39ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b295bee6217742e93114d8f9161857750f0873e","tid":731393,"uid":25062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T06:49:53.000Z","msg":"個樣都唔女孩了"},{"pid":"6c01a41192aa733297077bcd3140671ca9c3d7c0","tid":731393,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T06:51:09.000Z","msg":"真勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0341c1a8d26dc24bab575c003f6f58c7d6445b5d","tid":731393,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c01a41192aa733297077bcd3140671ca9c3d7c0","tid":731393,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T06:51:09.000Z","msg":"真勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T06:51:37.000Z","msg":"molamola"},{"pid":"62e9466dccf3f58e09fdb1f7ef39f15a22b74029","tid":731393,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:36:41.000Z","msg":"呢招o係香港玩就一定無事，自己印一張自己點整都無犯法"}]}